hadiths[43]{hadithnumber,text}:
2517,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jis shakhs ne bhi kisi musalman ( ghulam ( ko aazad kya to Allah Taala us ghulam ke jism ke har uzu (ang) ki aazadi ke badley us shakhs ke jism ke bhi eik-eik uzu (ang) ko dozakh se aazad karega. Saeed-bin-Marjaana ne bayan kya ke phir main Ali-bin Husain (Zainul-Aabedeen (rh)) ke yahan gaya (aur unse hadis bayan ki) wo apne aik ghulam ki taraf mutwajjeh huey. jiski Abdullaah-bin-Ja'far das hazaar dirham ya aik hazaar Dinar qeemat de rahe they aur aap ne usey aazad kar diya.
2518,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke kon sa amal afzal hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah par eman lana aur uski raah mein jihad karna. maine puchha aur kis tarah ka ghulam aazad karna afzal hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jo sabse zyada qeemtii ho aur Malik ki nazar mein jo bahut zyada pasandida ho. maine arz kya ke agar mujh se ye na ho sakaa? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ke phir kisi musalman kaareegar ki madad kar ya kisi be-hunar ki. unhon-ne kaha ke agar main ye bhi na kar sakaa? is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir logon ko apne shar se mehfooz kar de ke ye bhi aik sadqa hai jisey tum khud apne uper karogey."
2519,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne suraj girahan ke waqt ghulam aazad karne ka hukm farmaya hai. Musa ke sath us hadis ko Ali-bin madeenii ne bhi Abdul-Azeez darawardi se riwayat kya hai. unhon-ne Hisham se.
2520,hamein suraj girahan ke waqt ghulam aazad karne ka hukm diya jata tha.
2521,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya 2 saajhiyon ke darmyan saajhey ke ghulam ko agar kisi aik saajhii ne aazad kya, to agar aazad karne wala maaldaar hai to baqi hisson ki qeemat ka andaza kya jaeyga phir (usi ki taraf se) poorey ghulam ko aazad kar diya jaeyga"
2522,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jisne kisi mushtarak ghulam main apne hissey ko aazad kar diya aur uske paas itna maal hai ke ghulam ki poori qeemat ada ho sakey to uski qeemat insaf ke sath lagai jaeygi aur baqi saajhiyon ko unke hissey ki qeemat (usi ke maal se) de kar ghulam ko usi ki taraf se aazad kar diya jaeyga warna ghulam ka jo hissey aazad ho chuka wo ho chukaa. baqi hisson ki aazadi ke liye ghulam ko khud koshish karke qeemat ada karni hogi.
2523,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jisne kisi mushtarak ghulam ke apne hissey ko aazad kya aur uske paas ghulam ki poori qeemat ada karne ke liye maal bhi hai to pura ghulam usey aazad karaanaa lazim hai lekin agar uske paas itna maal na ho jis se poorey ghulam ki sahi qeemat ada ki ja sakey. to phir ghulam ka jo hissey aazad ho gaya wahi aazad hua. ham se Musaddad ne bayan kya, unse Bishr ne bayan kya aur unse Ubaidullah ne ikhtisar ke saath."
2524,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jisne kisi ( saajhey ( ghulam ka apna hissey aazad kar diya. ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) ye alfaz farmaaey (شركا له في عبد) ( shak rawi hadis Ayub sakhtiyan ko hua) aur uske paas itna maal bhi tha jis se poorey ghulam ki munasib qeemat ada ki ja sakti thi to wo ghulam poori tarah aazad samjha jaeyga (baqi hisson ki qeemat usko deeni hogi) Naafe ne bayan kya warna uska jo hissey aazad ho gaya bas wo aazad ho gaya. Ayub ne kaha ke mujhey malum nahi ye (aakhirii tukdaa) khud Naafe ne apni taraf se kaha tha ya ye bhi hadis mein shamil hai.
2525,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ghulam ya baandi ke barey mein ye fatwa diya kartey they ke agar wo kai saajhiyon ke darmyan mushtarak ho aur aik Sharik apna hissey aazad kar de to ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey they ke us shakhs par poorey ghulam ke aazad karaaney ki zimme-dari hogi lekin ye is sura mein jab shakhs mazkoor ke paas itna maal ho jis se poorey ghulam ki qeemat ada ki ja sakey. ghulam ki munasib qeemat laga kar doosrey saajhiyon ko unke hisson ke mutabiq adaaeygi kar di jaeygi aur ghulam ko aazad kar diya jaeyga ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ye fatwa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se naql kartey they aur Lais-bin-abii-Zi'ib, ibn-Is'haaq, Juweriya, Yahya-bin-Saeed aur Ismaaeel-bin-Umayya bhi Naafe se us hadis ko riwayat kartey hain, wo Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mukhtasar taur par."
2526,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne kisi ghulam ka aik hissey aazad kya.''
2527,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne kisi saajhey ke ghulam ka apna hissey aazad kya to uski poori aazadi usi ke zimma hai. basharte ke uske paas maal ho. warna ghulam ki qeemat lagai jaeygi aur (us se apne Baqiiya hisson ki qeemat ada karne ki) koshish ke liye kaha jaeyga lekin is par koi sakhti na ki jaaeygii.'' Saeed ke sath us hadis ko hujjaaj-bin-Hujjaaj, Aban aur Moosaa-bin-khalaf ne bhi Qatada se riwayat kya. Shoba ne isey mukhtasar kar diya hai."
2528,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala ne meri ummat ke dilon mein paida hone-waale waswason ko maaf kar diya hai jab tak wo unhein amal ya zaban par na laaein.''
2529,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aa'maal ka madaar niyat par hai aur har shakhs ko uski niyat ke mutabiq phal milta hai. to jiski hijrat Allah aur uske rasool ke liye ho, wo Allah aur uske rasool ke liye samjhii jaeygi aur jiski hijrat duniya ke liye hogi ya kisi aurat se shadi karne ke liye to ye hijrat mahz usi ke liye hogi jiski niyat se us ne hijrat ki hai.''"
2530,"jab wo Islam qabool karne ke iraadey se (Madina ke liye) nikley to unke sath unka ghulam bhi tha. ( rastey mein) wo donon aik doosrey se bichhad gaey. phir jab Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) (Madina pahunchne ke baad) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein baithey huey they, to unka ghulam bhi achcha aa gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Abu-Hurera ! ye lo tumhara ghulam bhi aa gaya. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, ya Rasulullah! main aapko gawah banata hun ke ye ghulam ab aazad hai. rawi ne kaha ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Madina pahunch kar ye sher kahey they. hai pyari bhale hi kathin hai aur lambi meri raat, par dilai us ne daarul-kufr se mujh ko najaat."
2531,"jab main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua tha to aatey huey rastey mein ye sher kaha tha : hai pyari bhale hi kathin hai aur lambi meri raat, par dilai us ne daarul-kufr se mujh ko najaat. unhon-ne bayan kya ke rastey mein mera ghulam mujh se bichhad gaya tha. phir jab main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Islam par qaaim rehney ke liye maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait kar li. mein abhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas betha hi hua tha ke wo ghulam dikhai diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, abu-Huraira! ye dekh tera ghulam bhi aa gaya. maine kaha, ya Rasulullah! wo Allah ke liye aazad hai. phir maine usey aazad kar diya. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) farmatey hain ke abu-Kuraib ne (apni riwayat mein) abu-Usama se ye lafz nahi riwayat kya ke wo aazad hai."
2532,"jab Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aa rahe they, to unke sath unka ghulam bhi tha, aap Islam ke iraadey se aa rahe they. achcha rastey mein wo ghulam bhool kar alag ho gaya (phir yahi hadis bayan ki) usmein yun hai aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tha, main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko gawah banata hun ke wo Allah ke liye hai."
2533,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya Utba-bin- abii-waqaas ne apne bhai Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ko wasiiyat ki thi ke Zam-aa ki baandi ke bachchey ko apne qabzey mein ley lein. usne kaha tha ke wo ladka mera hai. phir jab fateh Makka ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Makka) tashrif laaey, to Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne Zam-aa ki baandi ke ladkey ko ley liya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, abd-bin-Zam'a bhi sath they. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! ye mere bhai ka ladka hai, unhon-ne mujhey wasiiyat ki thi ke ye unhiin ka ladka hai. lekin abd-bin-Zam'a ne arz kya. ya Rasulullah! ye mera bhai hai. jo Zam-aa (mere waalid) ki baandi ka ladka hai. unhiin ke ''faraash'' par paida hua hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zam-aa ki baandi ke ladkey ko dekha to waqei wo Utba ki sura par tha. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey abd-bin-Zam'a! ye tumhari parwarish mein rahega. kyonke bachcha tumharey walid hi ke ''farsh'' par paida hua hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sath hi ye bhi farma diya ke ''aey Sauda-bin-Zam'a ! us se parda kya kar ''ye hidayat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isliye ki thi ke bachchey mein Utba ki shabaahat dekh li thi. Sauda (Raziallahu anha) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki biwi thin."
2534,ham mein se aik shakhs ne apni maut ke baad apne ghulam ki aazadi ke liye kaha tha. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us ghulam ko bulaya aur usey bech diya. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir wo ghulam apni aazadi ke pahley hi saal mar gaya tha.
2535,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 'walaa' ke bechney aur uske hiba karne se mana farmaya tha.
2536,"Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko maine khareedaa to unke maalikon ne 'walaa' ki shart lagai (ke aazadi ke baad wo unhein ke haq mein qaaim rahegii) maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum unhein aazad kar do, 'walaa' to usi ki hoti hai jo qeemat de kar kisi ghulam ko aazad kar de. phir maine unhein aazad kar diya. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya aur unke shauhar ke silsiley mein unhein ikhtiyar diya. Barira ne kaha ke agar wo mujhey falan-falan cheez bhi diin tab bhi mein uske paas na rahoongii. chunanche wo apne shauhar se juda ho gaiin."
2537,Ansar ke kuchh logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mulaqat ki aur ijazat chahi aur aa kar arz kya ke aap hamein uski ijazat de dijiye ke ham apne bhaanjey Abbas ka fidya maaf kar dein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi aik dirham bhi na chhodo.
2538,Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne kufr ke zamaney mein so ghulam aazad kiye they aur so oont logon ki sawari ke liye diye they. phir jab Islam laey to so oont logon ki sawari ke liye diye aur so ghulam aazad kiye. phir unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochha. ya Rasulullah ! kuchh un nek aamaal ke mutaalliq aap ka kya khayal hai jinhein main sawab ki niyat se kufr ke zamane mein kya karta tha. unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ''jo nekiyan tum pahley kar chukey ho wo sab qaaim rahengii.''
2539,"jab qabila Hawazin ki bhejey huey log (muslmaan ho kar) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khadey ho kar unse mulaqat farmai, phir un logon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney darkhaast ki ke unke amwaal aur qaidi wapas kar diye jaaein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey (khutba sunaayaa) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum dekhtey ho mere sath jo log hain (mein akelaa hota to tum ko wapas kar detaa) aur baat wahi mujhey pasand hai jo sach ho. isliye 2 chizon mein se aik hi tumhen ikhtiyar karni hogi, ya apna maal wapas ley lo, ya apne qaidiyon ko chhudaa lo, isi liye maine unki taqseem mein bhi der ki thii.'' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Taaif se laut'tey huey (Ja'araana mein) Hawazin walon ka wahan par kai raaton tak intizar kya tha. jab un logon par ye baat poori tarah zahir ho gaee ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 chizon (maal aur qaidi) mein se sirf aik hi ko wapas farma saktey hain. to unhon-ne kaha ke hamein hamarey aadmi hi wapas kar dijiye jo aap ki qaid mein hain. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon se Khattab farmaya, Allah ki tareef uski shaan ke mutabiq karne ke baad farmaya ''ammaa ba'd! ye tumharey bhai hamarey paas naadim ho kar aaey hain aur mera bhi khayal ye hai ke unke aadmi jo hamari qaid mein hain, unhein wapas kar diye jaaein. ab jo shakhs apni khushi se unke aadmiyon ko wapas karey wo aisa kar ley aur jo shakhs apne hissey ko chhodnaa na chahey (aur us shart par apne qaidiyon ko aazad karne ke liye taiyaar ho ke un qaidiyon ke badley mein) ham usey uske baad sabse pehli maale-ghanimat mein se jo Allah Taala hamein dega iske (is ( hissey ka badla iske hawale kar dengey to wo aisa kar ley.'' log is par bol padey ke ham apni khushi se qaidi ko wapas karne ke liye taiyaar hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ''lekin ham par ye zahir na ho saka ke kis ne hamein ijazat di hai aur kis ne nahi di hai. isliye sab log (apne khemon mein) wapas jayen aur sab ke zimmedaar aa kar unki raey se hamein aagah karein.'' chunanche sab log chaley aaey aur unke sardaaron ne (unse guftgu ki) phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar di ke sab ne apni khushi se ijazat de di hai. yahi wo khabar hai jo hamein Hawazin ke qaidiyon ke silsiley mein malum hui hai. (Zohri ne kaha) aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (jab Bahrain se maal aayaa) kaha tha ke (badr ke mauqe par) maine apna bhi fidya diya tha aur Aqeel (Raziallahu anhu) ka bhii."
2540,"jab qabila Hawazin ki bhejey huey log (muslmaan ho kar) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khadey ho kar unse mulaqat farmai, phir un logon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney darkhaast ki ke unke amwaal aur qaidi wapas kar diye jaaein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey (khutba sunaayaa) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum dekhtey ho mere sath jo log hain (mein akelaa hota to tum ko wapas kar detaa) aur baat wahi mujhey pasand hai jo sach ho. isliye 2 chizon mein se aik hi tumhen ikhtiyar karni hogi, ya apna maal wapas ley lo, ya apne qaidiyon ko chhudaa lo, isi liye maine unki taqseem mein bhi der ki thii.'' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Taaif se laut'tey huey (Ja'araana mein) Hawazin walon ka wahan par kai raaton tak intizar kya tha. jab un logon par ye baat poori tarah zahir ho gaee ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 chizon (maal aur qaidi) mein se sirf aik hi ko wapas farma saktey hain. to unhon-ne kaha ke hamein hamarey aadmi hi wapas kar dijiye jo aap ki qaid mein hain. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon se Khattab farmaya, Allah ki tareef uski shaan ke mutabiq karne ke baad farmaya ''ammaa ba'd! ye tumharey bhai hamarey paas naadim ho kar aaey hain aur mera bhi khayal ye hai ke unke aadmi jo hamari qaid mein hain, unhein wapas kar diye jaaein. ab jo shakhs apni khushi se unke aadmiyon ko wapas karey wo aisa kar ley aur jo shakhs apne hissey ko chhodnaa na chahey (aur us shart par apne qaidiyon ko aazad karne ke liye taiyaar ho ke un qaidiyon ke badley mein) ham usey uske baad sabse pehli maale-ghanimat mein se jo Allah Taala hamein dega iske (is ( hissey ka badla iske hawale kar dengey to wo aisa kar ley.'' log is par bol padey ke ham apni khushi se qaidi ko wapas karne ke liye taiyaar hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ''lekin ham par ye zahir na ho saka ke kis ne hamein ijazat di hai aur kis ne nahi di hai. isliye sab log (apne khemon mein) wapas jayen aur sab ke zimmedaar aa kar unki raey se hamein aagah karein.'' chunanche sab log chaley aaey aur unke sardaaron ne (unse guftgu ki) phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar di ke sab ne apni khushi se ijazat de di hai. yahi wo khabar hai jo hamein Hawazin ke qaidiyon ke silsiley mein malum hui hai. (Zohri ne kaha) aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (jab Bahrain se maal aayaa) kaha tha ke (badr ke mauqe par) maine apna bhi fidya diya tha aur Aqeel (Raziallahu anhu) ka bhii."
2541,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Banu-Mustaliq par jab hamla kya to wo bilkul ghaafil they aur unke maweshii pani pi rahe they. unke ladney walon ko qatl kya gaya, aurton bachchon ko qaid kar liya gaya. unhiin qaidiyon mein Juweriya (Raziallahu anhu) (ummul-momeneen) bhi thin. (Naafe (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne likha tha ke) ye hadis mujh se Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan ki thi, wo khud bhi Islami fauj ke sath they."
2542,"maine abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha to unse aik sawal kya, aap ne jawab mein kaha ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jange-banii-mustaliq ke liye nikley. us ghazwey mein hamein (qabeela bani mustaliq ke) Arab qaidi hath aaey (raastey hi mein) hamein aurton ki khahish hui aur aurat se alag rehna ham ko mushkil ho gaya. ham ne chaha ke azl kar lein. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us barey mein puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, tum azl kar saktey ho, usmein koi qabahat nahi lekin jin ruhon ki bhi qiyamat tak ke liye paidaaish muqaddar ho chuki hai wo to zaroor paida ho kar rahengii (lihaazaa tumhara azl karna bekaar hai)."
2543,"mein banu- Tameem se hamesha mohabbat karta raha hun (doosri sanad imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ( mujh se ibne-Salaam ne bayan kya, kaha ham ko Jarir bin-Abdul-Hameed ne khabar di, unhein Mughira ne, unhein Haris ne, unhein Abu-Zaraa ne aur unhein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne, (teesri sanad) aur Mughira ne Umara se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Abu-Zaraa se ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, teen baton ki wjah se jinhein maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai. main banu- Tameem se hamesha mohabbat karta hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke barey mein farmaya ke ye log dajjal ke muqaabley mein meri ummat mein sabse zyada sakht mukhalif Sabit hongey. unhon-ne bayan kya ke (eik martaba ( banu- Tameem ke yahan se zakat ( wsool ho kar aai ( to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye hamari qaum ki zakat hai. banu- Tameem ki aik aurat qaid ho kar Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas thi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke usey aazad kar do ke ye Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki aulad mein se hai."
2544,"ham se Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne bayan kya, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin-Fuzail se suna, unhon-ne Mutarrif se, unhon-ne Shabi se, unhon-ne abu-Barda se, unhon-ne abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se ke jis shakhs k paas koi londi ho aur wo uski achi parwarish karey aur uskey sath achchhaa maamlaa karey, phir usey aazad karkey ussey nikah kar ley to usko dohra sawab milega."
2545,"maine Abu-Zar Ghifari (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unke badan par bhi aik joda tha aur unke ghulam ke badan par bhi usi qism ka aik joda tha. ham ne uski wajah puchha to unhon-ne batlaya ke aik baar meri aik sahib (yani Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se) se kuchh gali galoch ho gaee thi. unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se meri shikayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se puchha ke kya tum ne unhein unki maa ki taraf se aar dilai hai? phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, tumharey ghulam bhi tumharey bhai hain agarche Allah Taala ne unhein tumhari ma-tehti mein de rakha hai. isliye jiska bhi koi bhai uske qabza mein ho usey wahi khilaey jo wo khud khata hai aur wahi pehnaey jo wo khud pehnta hai aur un par unki taqat se zyada bojh na daley. lekin agar unki taqat se zyada bojh dalo to phir unki khud madad bhi kar diya karo."
2546,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ghulam jo apne aaqa ka khair-khaah bhi ho aur apne rab ki ibadat bhi achi tarah karta ho to usey 2 guna sawab milta hai.''
2547,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jis kisi ke paas bhi koi baandi ho aur wo usey poorey Husn w khoobi ke sath adab sikhaaey, phir aazad karke us se shadi kar ley to usey 2 guna sawab milta hai aur jo ghulam Allah Taala ke huquq bhi ada karey aur apne malikon ke bhi to usey bhi 2 guna sawab milta hai."
2548,"unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ghulam jo kisi ki milkiyat mein ho aur neko kaar ho to usey 2 sawab miltey hain.'' aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai agar Allah Taala ke rastey mein jihad , Haj aur walida ki khidmat (ki rok) na hoti to main pasand karta ke ghulam reh kar maroon."
2549,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' kitna achchha hai kisi ka wo ghulam jo apne rab ki ibadat tamam husno-khubi ke sath bajaa laey aur apne Malik ki khair-khahi bhi karta rahe. ''
2550,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab ghulam apne aaqa ki khair-khahi karey aur apne rab ki ibadat tamam husno-khubi ke sath bajaa laey to usey 2 guna sawab milta hai.''
2551,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' ghulam jo apne rab ki ibadat behtreen tareeqey ke sath bajaa laey aur apne aaqa ke jo is par khair-khahi aur farmaan-bardaarii (ke huquq hain) unhein bhi ada karta rahe, to usey 2 guna sawab milta hai.''"
2552,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''koii shakhs (kisi ghulam ya kisi bhi shakhs se) ye na kahey. apne rab ( murad aaqa ( ko khana khilaa, apne rab ko wuzu karaa, apne rab ko pani pilaa''. balke sirf mere sardaar, mere aaqa ke alfaz kehna chahiye isi tarah koi shakhs ye na kahey .'' mera banda, meri bandii, balke yun kehna chahiye mera chhokraa, meri chhokrii, mera ghulaam.''"
2553,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne ghulam ka apna hissey aazad kar diya, aur uske paas itna maal bhi ho jis se ghulam ki waajibii qeemat ada ki ja sakey to usi ke maal se pura ghulam aazad kya jaeyga warna jitna aazad ho gaya ho gayaa.''"
2554,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum mein se har shakhs Hakim hai aur uski riaya ke barey mein sawal hoga. to logon ka waqei ameer aik Hakim hai aur us se uski riaya ke barey mein sawal hoga aur har aadmi apne ghar walon par Hakim hai aur us se uski riaya ke barey mein sawal hoga aur aurat apne shauhar ke ghar aur uske bachchon par Hakim hai us se uski riaya ke barey mein sawal hoga aur ghulam apne aaqa (saiyed) ke maal ka Hakim hai aur us se uski raiyat ke barey mein sawal hoga. to jaan lo ke tum mein se har aik Hakim hai aur har aik se uski raiyat ke barey mein (qiyamat ke din) poochh hogi. ''
2555,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab baandi zina kiraaey to usey ( bataur had sharaee ( kode lagaao phir agar karey to usey kode lagaao teesri ya chothi baar mein (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) phir usey bech do, chahe qeemat mein aik rassii hi miley.''"
2556,"nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab baandi zina kiraaey to usey ( bataur had sharaee ( kode lagaao phir agar karey to usey kode lagaao teesri ya chothi baar mein (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) phir usey bech do, chahe qeemat mein aik rassii hi miley.''"
2557,maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke jab kisi ka ghulam khana laey aur wo usey apne sath (khilaaney ke liye) na bitha sakey to usey aik ya 2 niwaaley zaroor khilaa de ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( لقمة أو لقمتين (ke badal ( أكلة أو أكلتين ( farmaya (yani aik ya 2 luqmey ( kyonke usi ne usko taiyaar karne ki takleef uthai hai.
2558,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''har aadmi Hakim hai aur us se uski riaya ke barey mein sawal hoga. imam Hakim hai aur us se uski raiyat ke barey mein sawal hoga. mard apne ghar ke maamlaat ka afsar hai aur us se uski riaya ke barey mein sawal hoga. aurat apne shauhar ke ghar ki afsar hai aur us se uski riaya ke barey mein sawal hoga. khaadim apne aaqa (saiyed (ke maal ka muhaafiz hai aur us se uske barey mein sawal hoga.'' unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye baatein suni hain aur mujhey khayal hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye bhi farmaya tha ke mard apne bap ke maal ka muhaafiz hai aur usse uski raiyat ke barey mein sawal hoga. gharaz tum mein se har fard Hakim hai aur sabse uski raiyat ke barey mein sawal hoga."
2559,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab koi kisi se jhagdaa karey to chehrey (par maarney) se parhez kare.''
